        "action": "Stop ESA being taken \u00a3 for \u00a3 off peoples Universal Credit Payments",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "ESA is paid to people in need and mostly to people too sick to work, for UC claimants you are penalised \u00a3 for \u00a3 and are no better off at the end. ESA should be kept a separate benefit for the sick and most in need just like PIP and DLA and if not then UC claimants should not be penalised for this",
